e Ecobee Premium offers superior accuracy, advanced sensors, and better long-term reliability for your comfort control needs. Key Sources: Google Nest Temperature Sensor Settings Wirecutter Thermostat Reviews Ecobee Accuracy Specifications Would you like me to create a detailed installation guide for whichever option you choose? https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/reviews/the-best-thermostat/ i have a guest furnace with baseboard.Heating, so it's a hot water and baseboard.Heat circulating system, which is the best.Thermostat, for this type of system, I do not have hvac or cooling. only heat Perfect! For a hydronic (hot water) baseboard heating system, you need a line voltage thermostat specifically designed for boiler systems. Let me analyze the best options for your specific setup. Using Tool | Search best smart thermostat hydronic baseboard heating boiler system line voltage 2024 View Using Tool | Search Mysa Smart Thermostat v2 hydronic baseboard heating compatibility review View Using Tool | Search Honeywell T87RF wireless thermostat hydronic heating boiler control View Let me get more specific information about low-voltage thermostats for hydronic systems. Using Tool | Search \"low voltage thermostat\" \"hydronic baseboard\" \"boiler control\" 24V smart thermostat View Using Tool | Search Ecobee Nest hydronic boiler heating system compatibility 24V low voltage View Let me get specific information about the exact setup for hydronic baseboard systems. Using Tool | Read https://tonytantillo.com/best-thermostat-for-hydronic-baseboard-heating/ View Using Tool | Read https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OFSQEQ4aB84 View Based on my research, I have excellent news! For your hydronic (hot water) baseboard heating system, you have several excellent smart thermostat options. Let me provide you with a comprehensive tactical analysis. Critical System Analysis First, let me clarify your system type: Hydronic baseboard heating = Hot water circulating through baseboards NOT electri